T1 - Phylogeography of Aedes ( Stegomyia ) aegypti (L.) and Aedes ( Stegomyia ) albopictus (Skuse) (Diptera: Culicidae) based on mitochondrial DNA variations
JA - Genetical Research
VL - 86
